WESTERN SOUTH ATLANTIC.
URUGUAY.

   12 7000 METER LONG CABLES ALONG TRACKLINE BETWEEN
   35-24.57S 052-07.65W AND 36-21.60S 053-04.87W.

3. CANCEL THIS MSG 04 MAR 14.
